Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.47,0:02:41.64,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}Holding to the creed and blade to slay thee
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.64,0:02:44.81,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}Carry on the oath until my last scene
